name: SINS IN HELL
description:
Hey, my sweety-meaty leather bags.


Today I want to ask you - do you have Sins?

Probably, you 'll immediately begin to sort out in your head everything 
for which you can be punched in the ass with a belt, 
but you will not remember the real sins, people are weak.

And try to forget everything that they do not like. 
Reasonable, lol.

Remember one thing:

Sins are a multi-headed Hydra, the more heads you cut off, 
the more they grow.
Only hunger 'll kill the Hydra.




Catching up on what I mean?





:: visuals: @cryptohamster | sound-design: @zokart_3000
